                    <note>Taken from <ref type="mss" corresp="ESmhg014">ESP (UH) MHG-014; f. 15V.</ref>.</note>
                    <ab>ስምዑ፡ ዘገብረት፡ ሎቱ፡ ለገብረ፡ ዜአሃ፡፡ ዘይሰመይ፡ ገብረ፡ ማርያ፡ ወአምጽአት፡ ሎቱ፡ መንበረ፡ ዘወርቅ፡ ዘይሠርቁ፡ ቦቱ፡ ፲ወ፪፡ ብርሃናት፡ ወቦቱ፡ ባዕበ፡ ይሠርቁ፡ ፲ወ፪፡ ከዋከፍት፡ ወይመስል፡ ለውእቱ፡ መንበር፡ ክበቡ፡ ከመ፡</ab>
                </div>
            </div><!--  
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <note>Translated by Jeremy Brown and Wendy Laura Belcher <ref type="mss" corresp="ESP014">ESP (UH) MHG-014; f. 15v, in 2022.</note>
             <ab>A miracle [performed] by Our Lady Mary, Mariham, may her prayer and blessing be with her servant, forever and ever, amen.
Listen to what she has done for her servant named Gabra Maryam!
She brought him a golden throne that shone with twelve lights and twelve stars. And this throne was rounded like a bowl.
She also showed him a bright city and its light was like nothing anyone had seen before that day.
[She also said,] "You will remain in the thoughts of the Holy Trinity."
Gabra Maryam replied, "But who will enter into this city and sit on this throne?"
And she said to him, "Those who eagerly love to praise her will enter this city and will sit on this throne. And you will be their leader."
And having said this, she blessed him and she ascended into heaven.
May her intercession be with her servant, forever and ever, Amen.</ab>
